  <name>Xpano</name>
  <summary>Easy panorama stitching</summary>
  <branding>
    <color type="primary" scheme_preference="light">#9de185</color>
    <color type="primary" scheme_preference="dark">#344a2c</color>
  </branding>
  <description>
    <p>
      Xpano is a photo stitching tool that focuses on simplicity and ease of use, you can use it to:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Auto detect groups of images that can be stitched into panoramas</li>
      <li>Quickly preview the results with zoom and pan</li>
      <li>Crop, auto fill boundaries and select from multiple projection types</li>
      <li>Adjust the projection parameters: pitch, yaw and roll</li>
      <li>Export full resolution panoramas, including exif metadata</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
